==The Glove Doesn't Fit==
[[Image:Daddy taught me how to shoot.jpg|thumb|right|Ah, the irony of it all...]]
Upon learning that he just killed a fellow wigger, Jimenez proceeded to panic like any good retard would. He took off down another alleyway and stopped at [[Tom Serson]]'s on the way to buy more shitty weed that would replace what [[Attention whore|Riley]] stole from him (damn Juggalos and their dead babies). As he departed from the neighborhood pedo's domicile, he spotted [[Sesame Street|Oscar the Grouch]] who really needed to buy an untraceable pistol. Jimenez saw an opportunity and sold Oscar the gun [[Truth|he just used to shoot his gay lover with]] for $50, thus making back the cash he had to spend to buy [[Santorum|Tommy Boy's product]].

After stopping at a dive bar in Philly to drink [[Piss|Nyquil]] and swallow massive amounts of [[Jenkem|Coricidin]], Jimenez rode [[Nigga_stole_my_bike|a stolen bicycle home]] and woke [[Girlvinyl|Mommy Dearest]] up at midnight '''[[SRSLY]]''' with a confession that not even Dr. Phil would believe.

