==The Aftermath==

Shit got crazy quick. One of the local dirty [[Ann Coulter|whores]] reported to the [[ACLU|cops]] that she heard the blood gushing out of Riley's neck. This is similar to hearing [[PixelBeeProductions]]' orgasm noises, which induces immediate death. It is rumored that [[Black Jesus|Black Jesus]] also heard the flow of blood and was thought to have remarked, "That's some funny shit!" before hitting the crack pipe and taking off in Air Force One to do [[Holocaust|WTC 2.0]] on the Kennedy Compound. Even black person put her two cents in on [[Fox News]], commenting that [[Islam|counseling]] may have been the higher road.

==Cops + Wiggers = IRL BANHAMMER==

After pwning your [[Dorian Thorn|buttbuddy]] in an alleyway, the [[You|average person]] wouldn't go back to the crime scene. But that is exactly what our future an hero did!  Jimenez was quickly picked up by an alert [[mark Foley|cop]] after he was spotted with [[Semen|blood]] on his hands. Under threat of assrape he gave up the location of the gun, all the while [[NO U|denying ever shooting Riley]] despite numerous eyewitness accounts. Plus he was seen placing a bullet in the firing chamber after pulling back the gun slide, thus qualifying Jimenez for the much coveted '''Tard of The Year''' award.

As of now Jimenez is being held at the Montgomery County Correctional Facility [http://mccf.montcopa.org/mccf/site/default.asp in lieu of bail].

